        <num>CCP 1881</num>
        <heading>1881.  Construction</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1881.  Construction
Articles 1871 through 1883 are declared to be remedial.  Their purpose is to settle and afford relief from uncertainty and insecurity with respect to rights, status, and other legal relations, and they are to be liberally construed and administered.</p>
        </content>
